r does the 28 laps a day it will equal the distance they are crossing, 7700 nautical miles = 8861.01 miles," says a Hapag-Lloyd Cruises spokesperson.Europa — Hapag-Lloyd CruisesThis ship is on course to Barbados, scheduled to arrive April 3. This voyage is also taking place to get the ship to its appropriate hold position.             CNN
